---
title: Caribbean Pork & Kumara Fries with Caramelised Pineapple Salsa
description: We’ve packed the signature flavours of the Caribbean into this pork dish with mild jerk seasoning and a sweetly tangy caramelised pineapple salsa, but we think the homemade kumara fries on the side might just be the best bit!
